{"id":279088,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/【首发】年初三广东湛江两村械斗一死三重伤三车/","date":"2013-02-14T07:45:39Z","modified":"2013-02-14T07:45:39Z","title":"【首发】年初三广东湛江两村械斗一死三重伤三车被砸翻 警鸣枪警告 (10图)","content":"<p><a name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<div><span>2013</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">年</span><span>2</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">月</span><span>12</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日年初三，广东湛江吴川市塘缀镇，爆发严重集体械斗事件。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">中堂村因纠纷欲砍湛屋村，一翟屋村村民被点错相遭砍伤。翟屋村</span><span>报</span><span>复，引发中翟两村的大械斗。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">一</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">中堂村村民被刺中大腿动脉后，送往湛江医院抢救，途中因失血过多死亡，三村民亦被砍至重伤，一被虏走。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">派出所所长龙贵往翟屋村救人，被村民包围打伤，期间有警员鸣枪警告。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>13</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">日年初四，两村在顿谷村委会再爆冲突，三辆车被砸翻。</span><span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">当局出动大批武警镇压，翟屋村大部分男丁已闻风逃走，目前事件仍在发展中。</span><span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ytF_5h-IZpo/URx_1R2HCQI/AAAAAAAASys/Zx1rHWXOE20/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"479\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ytF_5h-IZpo/URx_1R2HCQI/AAAAAAAASys/Zx1rHWXOE20/s640/1.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dEqTkXrEvk8/URx_3QFVk9I/AAAAAAAASy0/896-S9asz3E/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"480\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-dEqTkXrEvk8/URx_3QFVk9I/AAAAAAAASy0/896-S9asz3E/s640/2.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-c4GMYXaKYX4/URx_3ofU2pI/AAAAAAAASy4/JsLA--6JFUA/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"479\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-c4GMYXaKYX4/URx_3ofU2pI/AAAAAAAASy4/JsLA--6JFUA/s640/3.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qYARkgwyqik/URx_5n0J5aI/AAAAAAAASzE/xOPcovbEUhw/s1600/4.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"481\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-qYARkgwyqik/URx_5n0J5aI/AAAAAAAASzE/xOPcovbEUhw/s640/4.jpg\" width=\"640\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-WrnpWhsWWIY/URx_7FRntzI/AAAAAAAASzM/_Flg0TP7KYg/s1600/5.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"640\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-WrnpWhsWWIY/URx_7FRntzI/AAAAAAAASzM/_Flg0TP7KYg/s640/5.jpg\" width=\"480\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-NufQR10-9jQ/URx_8liB4YI/AAAAAAAASzU/LuudmKhoL-M/s1600/6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"640\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-NufQR10-9jQ/URx_8liB4YI/AAAAAAAASzU/LuudmKhoL-M/s640/6.jpg\" width=\"480\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Sb-pPI8MSPg/URx_9jty2eI/AAAAAAAASzc/e-k0gej4FDY/s1600/7.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"640\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Sb-pPI8MSPg/URx_9jty2eI/AAAAAAAASzc/e-k0gej4FDY/s640/7.jpg\" width=\"480\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-9xUIRgT7-vE/URx_-5UOkII/AAAAAAAASzk/h_aYYzBBWQs/s1600/8.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"640\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-9xUIRgT7-vE/URx_-5UOkII/AAAAAAAASzk/h_aYYzBBWQs/s640/8.jpg\" width=\"478\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-2qXoi2CilBo/URyAAlZgSSI/AAAAAAAASzs/oOcLhIpo5Hw/s1600/9.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"640\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-2qXoi2CilBo/URyAAlZgSSI/AAAAAAAASzs/oOcLhIpo5Hw/s640/9.jpg\" width=\"480\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-oXTjsUzQDW4/URyACyglltI/AAAAAAAASz0/aI6fZCfrfvU/s1600/10.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"640\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-oXTjsUzQDW4/URyACyglltI/AAAAAAAASz0/aI6fZCfrfvU/s640/10.jpg\" width=\"480\" /></a></div>\n<div><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\">中国茉莉花革命</span><span>http://www.molihua.org  </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">转载请注明出处</span><span></span></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17